      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二猎户同上，）"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户甲",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "官府有明文，猎户受灾星。倘若速严限，我等命难存。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我乃，阳谷县猎户是也。只因今日景阳岗上，出了一只吊睛白额猛虎，伤人无"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "数。本县太爷，立限悬了赏格，要我们捉获，但此虎十分凶猛，我们如何能拿"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得他来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，我们穿着虎皮衣服，伏在岭下，多多摆些窝弓药箭，待它自来送命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，我们就此前去，正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户乙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狭路难回避，官差不自由。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二猎户同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "猎户甲→猎户乙",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "念": 1,
          "白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      },
      "scene_feature": [
        0.0,
        0.0,
        0.7143,
        0.2857,
        0.1667,
