        0.0,
        0.0
      ]
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "一声吼",
        "万万去不得",
        "千人惊恐",
        "四猎户",
        "店家",
        "数步远众生含痛",
        "武松",
        "猎户丁",
        "猎户丙"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "道旁车马日纷纷，行路悠悠何足云。未知肝胆向谁诉，今日却忆平原君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，武松。久住在柴皇亲庄上，意欲投奔宋公明，为此别了柴大官人，一路直"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "往阳谷县寻俺哥哥，不免就此走遭也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（新水令） 老天何苦困英雄，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二十年一场春梦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只落得沸尘海，数千重。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "任鸟兔，枉措弄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "迤逦行来，已是景阳岗下了。呀，你看这一酒店，酒旗之上写着“三碗不过岗”，"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是怎么讲？想我行路饥渴，且进去少坐一会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店家哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（店家上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来哉，来哉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这酒酒酒，有有有，赊赊赊，走走走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人敢莫是吃酒的么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是喝酒的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此请里边坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店家我且问你，那酒招子上，写着“三碗不过岗”？"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我倒不信，有如此厉害？"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人不信，吃吃看，就晓得了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你去取来，待俺先吃它十几碗，看俺过得岗，过不得岗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我拿来你吃吃就晓得哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂，伙计们，拿一壶酒来吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人酒来哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是这个碗，待俺先吃三碗，与我斟上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斟上哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "干。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃的倒快呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人又斟上哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "干。斟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "燥些。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人，要拿点啥菜来过酒罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武松 （折桂令） 令又何须炙凤烹龙？"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个朋友，他倒喜欢吃寡酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斟来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无有哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么说？"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没白哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "才吃怎么就说没有了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们这个壶，有个定数，满满三碗，一滴也不多，一滴也不少。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，有酒只管拿来，什么三碗四碗！"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人海量，吃的高兴，待我拿一瓮来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，你快快去拿一瓮来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计们掇一瓮来吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待俺吃个爽快的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人，一瓮来哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得，待我打开泥头，喔呀，真正喷香扑鼻子，好琥珀颜色，"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（折桂令） 鹦鹉杯，浮琥珀光浓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "干，斟来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人的喉咙，好似退光漆的，真正光滑的很！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这酒，比前番却好多了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是原瓮头，一点金生丽也没有，比先前的力量，更大多了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "干。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人，已吃了五碗了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可知那五斗消愁。斟来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，满哉，满哉，嗳呀，客人快拿瓶子筛子来接接罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可惜，可惜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十粒米，才作的一滴滴，客人吃了九碗哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店家！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（折桂令） 三杯合道，自有神功，"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人吃的甚勇，舌头有些大了，还要吃么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多口，快斟来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人吃了十二碗了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（折桂令） 别人吃酒，何用你虚担怕恐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有人开饭店，哪怕大肚汉。吃吃吃，没有了，倒不出来哉，瓮底朝天了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有了么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿了去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我拿了去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好酒，却饮得爽快！"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒钱哩？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "酒钱么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多少？"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这一壶，一瓮，该银三钱六分七厘八毫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有就拿来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多蒙柴大官人，赐我的盘川，一路行来，剩不多了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店家，你拿去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿，想是银子在这包裹里面，待我打开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店家，就将这包裹，放在此处，改日来取。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "连包裹当押头，待我拿进去，收好了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "须放好了，改日来取。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "知道哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计们，将客人的包裹收起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，叫俺羞涩囊空。咳，上岗赶路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你往哪里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上岗去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去不得，去不得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么去不得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这岗上近日出了一只吊睛白额虎，吃人无数，官府大张告示，来往客商，必须"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要结伴成群，于巳、午、未三个时辰过岗，单身客人，不许行走，恐伤性命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "万万去不得、武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住口，你不说猛虎，俺不去也罢；你说起有猛虎，俺不觉精神抖擞，毛发倒竖，"
        },
        {
          "character": "万万去不得、武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺偏要前去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（店家拉武松。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去不得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你放手！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（折桂令） 按不住怒气冲冲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万去不得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，谁要你管！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松推店家，店家跌。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喔呀，老虎把你当瓜子吃，于我啥个事吓。我才不管你去不去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（店家下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武松 （折桂令） 俺只是形色匆匆，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "趁着这落日微熹，醉眼的朦胧"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这虎在哪里，虎在哪里？这些人尽是胡说，连官府的榜文，也是混帐，不免下"
        },
        {
          "character": "店家",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岗赶路。呵呀呀，这酒竟涌上来了！妙吓，这一块大石，俺且睡他娘一觉再走。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（虎形跳上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，好风！快活，呀，果然有个大虫来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（雁儿落） 觑着这泼毛团体势雄，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松打虎形，棍折两段。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（雁儿落） 狼牙棍，先摧迸！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（虎形三扑，武松三躲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武松 （雁儿落） 俺这里趋前退后忙，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这孽畜舞爪张牙横。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（虎形扑，武松躲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（得胜令） 闪闪得它回身处扑着空，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "转眼出乱着踪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因此上冤家对面逢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虎吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（得胜令） 你要显神通，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "便作道力，有千斤重。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日你遇着俺武松吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（得胜令） 途也么穷，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抵多少，花无百日红。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松打虎形死。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这畜生，要来寻俺，待我先将你两眼踢瞎，看你跑到哪里！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松踢虎形。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，怎么不动了？死了么？管它死不死，下岗赶路要紧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，又有两个大虫来了！俺武松，今番死也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（沽美酒） 只嗦逞余威斗晚风，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "逞余威斗晚风。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只见他双举步，两条腿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二猎户随猎户丙、猎户丁同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙、猎户丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，你是人是鬼，敢在此独自行走！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武松 （沽美酒） 俺便是盖世英雄，唤武松！"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙、猎户丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可曾遇着大虫？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们问的是那大虫么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙、猎户丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是，"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你等听着！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（沽美酒） 试言它凶猛，"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙、猎户丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙、猎户丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一声吼，千人惊恐"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙、猎户丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "数步远众生含痛"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武松 （沽美酒） 负隅处恁威风。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尾一剪，钢刀般横。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怎么不曾被他害了？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武松 （沽美酒） 俺呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "空拳儿，结果了这大虫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙、猎户丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来这虎，被你打死了。多谢，多谢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武松 （沽美酒） 呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫众口将俺称颂！"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙、猎户丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "实不相瞒我们是阳谷县的猎户，官府立了限期，要叫我们拿这只虎，我们近它"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙、猎户丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不得。今被你打死，我们却是不信。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们不信，随我来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 早难道，岩前虎瘦，雄心横，"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这不是虎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四猎户",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳哟哟，这样一只大虎，竟被你空拳打死。就是那卞庄、李存孝，也不如你！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武松 （尾声） 笑恁那提防镇日，也无用！"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如今你来得，可就去不得了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎样去不得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是吓，少不得要同你，去到县中领赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，请赏？"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙、猎户丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武松 （尾声） 俺本是逆旅经商，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁曾望，奏绩呈功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一定要去的，"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺若是去呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 怕只怕三街六巷，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前遮后拥，沸沸扬扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他说些什么呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他道阳谷县一个大虫，没有人打得，倒被俺清河县人打死。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 怕你那阳谷县人，相讥讽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "壮士，也叫我县中人认认，你这打虎的好汉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武松 （尾声） 好！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺正要到县中去寻俺的哥哥，正好相从。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙、猎户丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，把虎栓起来，先抬下岗去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（猎户甲、猎户乙抬虎行同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙、猎户丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "壮士请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位请，俺若不去——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 怎当得起他们恁趋恭！"
        },
        {
          "character": "猎户丙、猎户丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "壮士请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（武松、二猎户同下。）"
